    "description": "BigDFT-futile: a library handling most common FORTRAN low-level\noperations, like memory managment, profiling routines, I/O operations.\nIt also supports yaml output and parsing for fortran programs. It also\nprovides wrappers routines to MPI and linear algebra operations. This\nlibrary is intensively used in BigDFT packages.\n",
